{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "楚留香被豹姬释放时，面对珠宝、海上补给和奄奄一息的白云生三样礼物，舍弃最能自救的粮水而救下白云生。二人在海上几乎等死，后来凭楚留香从“麻子”身上搜出的旗花火箭发出史天王属下求救讯号，才被渔船救至孤岛渔村。数月后楚留香向胡铁花追述此事，并揭出渔村其实是史天王海上根据地之一，胡开树等名侠也在那里向史天王有所求。最终楚留香亲眼见到所谓史天王：他不是一个人，而是七个装束、步伐、气势几乎合一的人，这一真相令楚留香前所未有地震惊。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "你们的将军真的肯就这么样让我走?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "长腿的小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "当然是真的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "长腿的小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她既不想要那头豹子咬死你，也不想让它被你咬死，还留住你干什么?",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "她真是个痛快的女人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "长腿的小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她本来就是这样子的，不但痛快，而且大方，只要是她请来的客人，从来没有空手而回的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "难道她还准备了什么礼物让我带走?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "长腿的小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "她不但早就准备好了，而且还准备了三种，可是你只能选一种。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "哪三种?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "长腿的小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "第一种是价值八十万两的翡翠和珍珠。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "她真大方。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "长腿的小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "第二种是足够让你吃喝半个月的波斯葡萄酒和风鸡肉脯，还有一大桶清水。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "她想得真周到。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "第三样礼物是什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "长腿的小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "是个已经快要死了的人，简直差不多已经死定了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "长腿的女孩子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "将军知道你一定会选第二样的，因为你是个绝顶聪明的人。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "哦?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "长腿的女孩子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "可是将军又说，如果你选的是珠宝，那么你这个人不但贪心，而且愚蠢，连她都会对你很失望。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "如果我选的是第三样呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "长腿的女孩子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那么你简直就不是人，是条笨猪了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "长腿的女孩子",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你选哪一样?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "我告诉你一个秘密好不好?",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_chang_tui_de_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "我本来就不是人，是条猪。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yun_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白云生",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你看起来好像很高兴的样子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yun_sheng",
      "text": "好像是的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yun_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白云生",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我想不通，现在还有什么事能让你这么高兴?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yun_sheng",
      "text": "至少我们现在还活着。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yun_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白云生",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我们虽然还活着，也只不过在等死而已，有什么好高兴的?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yun_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白云生",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你为什么不选择你需要的粮食和水，反而救了我?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yun_sheng",
      "text": "你和豹姬都是史天王的人，她为什么会用这种方法对你?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那一次你怎么会没有死?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "因为有个人救了我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "在那种时候，那种地方，有谁会去救你?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你永远想不到的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "就连我自己都想不到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那个人究竟是谁?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这次你绝不能再要我猜了，我已经猜了三个月还没有猜出来，难道你真要把我活活急死?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "好，这次我告诉你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "那次救了我的人，就是那个要搜身的麻子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "是她救了你?她怎么会救你?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这件事其实也简单得很。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "她救了我，只不过因为我把她丢进了海里去。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "她要搜我，我当然也要搜一搜她，只不过对她那种女人，我实在没兴趣碰她，所以我用了种很特别的法子。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "什么法子?",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我先提起她的那双尊脚，把她身上的东西全都抖了出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "然后呢?",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "然后我只不过顺手摸鱼，把其中几样比较特别的东西给摸了过来。其中有一样是个像袖箭般的圆铁筒子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "就是这个圆筒子救了你?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "就是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "一个小小的圆筒子怎么能从大海中救人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "别的圆筒子不能，这个圆筒子能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这个圆筒子究竟是什么鬼玩意?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "也不是什么鬼玩意，只不过是一筒旗花火箭而已。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "白云生看见我把那个圆筒子拿出来的时候，脸上的表情，简直比你看到一千两百坛陈年好酒还要高兴。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "一个人如果能看到自己的朋友脸上露出那种表情来，一辈子只要看见一次也就够了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我知道你这个人运气一向都很不错，却还是没想到你的运气会有这么好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这不是运气。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这不是运气!难道你早就知道那个圆筒子是史天王属下遇难时用来呼救的讯号?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那么这不是运气是什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这只不过是一点点智慧、一点点谨慎、一点点处处留意的习惯，再加上一点点手法和技巧而已。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "除此之外，还有样东西当然也是少不了的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "什么东西?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "运气，当然是运气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "除了运气之外，难道还能有什么别的东西?",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我们把那一筒讯号放出不久，就有一批渔船来把我们救到一个孤岛上去，岛上只有一个渔村，居民都是渔夫，看起来和别的渔村完全没有什么两样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "可是我却在那个渔村里遇到几个奇怪的人，我永远想不到会在那种地方遇到他们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他们是谁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "胡开树、司徒平、金震甲和李盾。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这些大英雄大侠客们到那个小渔村里去干什么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我想他们大概不是去吃鱼的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你想呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "难道那个渔村就是史天王在海上的根据地之一，难道那些大侠们都是为了史天王而去的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "像你这样的聪明人，为什么偏偏会有人硬要说你笨?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我一直有点看不起那位胡大侠，想不到他居然真是个角色，居然也有胆子去找史天王。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你知不知道他为了什么要去找史天王?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "难道他不是去找史天王拼命的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "拼是拼命，只可惜拼的不是他自己的命。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他去找史天王，只不过要求史天王为他去拼掉几个人的命而已。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他是不是还带去一份重礼?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "那当然是绝不能少的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我一点都不奇怪，我真的一点都不奇怪，像这样的大侠我早就见得多了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我想他看到你的时候，脸上的表情一定也很有意思。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "老实说，那样的表情我也不想再看到第二次。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那一次史天王究竟有没有到那个渔村里去?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他当然去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你有没有看见他?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我又不瞎，怎么会看不见?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他是个怎么样的人?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我也不知道他是个什么样的人，我只能告诉你，我真正看清他的那一瞬间，我才明白别人为什么说他是杀不死的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "为什么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "因为他根本不是一个人。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yun_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白云生",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "大帅来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yun_sheng",
      "text": "大帅?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yun_sheng",
      "text": "哪一位大帅?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yun_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白云生",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这里只有一位大帅。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_bai_yun_sheng",
      "text": "你说的这位大帅就是史天王?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yun_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "白云生",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    }
